package: libhubo-motion-rt
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: libach1, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Libraries for interfacing with the Hubo-Motion-RT control architecture
  Hubo_Tech allows control commands to be sent to Hubo-Motion-RT's control daemon
  and provides a convenient interface with the daemonizer library.

